{
  "stem": "27347.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But he would never talk to me about this.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He would never talk to me about it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I used to interview my father for hours.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "If I didn't feel like sleeping, and instead of bed time stories which I knew already by heart, I used to ask him how do you make iron, or how you make glass, or where one thing or another comes from.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he used to have all the answers.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Of course, my father was the smartest man on earth.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I used to be very proud of him.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I did.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He said, 'No,' he says, 'It's politics.' 'It's politics.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Don't worry about it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Everything will be OK.'",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I certainly do.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I remember going to sleep, and in the morning the-- they communicated we are now part of Germany.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And stores, Jewish stores, right away looted, broken windows, and guess what?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My friends didn't like me anymore.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My gentile friends that I was very close and I loved, and I wanted to play with them and they didn't want me.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[SOBBING] I didn't understand it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was the first taste of discrimination.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And from there on it became worse.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I used to walk in the streets and if we saw a SS man or any uniformed German, you were supposed to say heil Hitler.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I was afraid not to say it, that they will harm me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[SOBBING] And I used to say it and feel unclean by doing that.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was-- I was frightened because every night in my sleep I was awakened by terrorizing Jews in the streets, men crying out from pain.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] It was terror.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It turned overnight into a nightmare.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Men with bearded men were beaten.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[SOBBING] Sometimes there'd be torn beards to the blood.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
